fabulous to model for me.

27
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,590
Somepony with beauty,

28
00:01:04,630 --> 00:01:06,170
somepony with grace,

29
00:01:06,170 --> 00:01:07,630
somepony...

30
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,010
like you?

31
00:01:09,050 --> 00:01:11,220
Oh, goodness.
I don't know.

32
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:14,060
Oh, this is
such a huge opportunity,

33
