ple-e-e-ase?!

41
00:01:31,370 --> 00:01:33,200
[ Ting! ]

42
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:37,040
Oh, if it's that important
to you, of course I'll do it.

43
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,920
