how you --

106
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:17,910
Twilight! You promised Spike
you wouldn't say anything.

107
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:20,290
He trusts you,
and losing a friend's trust

108
00:04:20,330 --> 00:04:21,980
