to lose a friend forever!

109
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:22,750
But --

110
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:25,070
Foreve-e-e-r!

111
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:27,540
My lips are sealed.

112
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,750
Though I'm pretty sure

113
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:31,340
Rarity is gonna pick up
on your feelings.

114
00:04:33,380 --> 00:04:34,930
[ Door opens, bell jingles ]

115
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:37,510
[ Foreign accent ]
I, Photo Finish...

116
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,890
