124
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:58,620
No!

125
00:04:58,660 --> 00:05:00,490
[ Whimpers ]

126
00:05:00,530 --> 00:05:01,830
Yes.

127
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,790
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

128
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,500
[ Ting! ]

129
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:06,960
No!

130
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,790
Yes.
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

131
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,550
No!

132
00:05:14,590 --> 00:05:16,630
Yes.

133
00:05:17,930 --> 00:05:19,470
Enough!

134
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,390
She hardly took
any pictures.

135
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,770
[ Tinkling ]

136
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:32,770
I'm so sorry.
I tried my best.

137
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:34,650
Well, the headdress
is too big for you,

138
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:35,990
and the cape
had too much sparkle.

139
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:39,360
I can't believe I ever thought
I could impress her.

140
00:05:39,410 --> 00:05:41,160
It seems that I,
Photo Finish,

141
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:44,080
have found the next fashion star
here in Ponyville.

142
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,500
Really?

143
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,790
Yes, really.

144
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:48,830
And I, Photo Finish,

145
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:53,670
am going to help her to shine
all over Eqvestria!

146
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:58,970
Tomorrow,
a photo shoot in ze park!

147
00:05:59,010 --> 00:05:59,970
I go!

148
00:06:00,010 --> 00:06:01,470
[ Zip! ]

149
00:06:02,100 --> 00:06:03,680
Did you hear that?

150
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:07,060
I am going to
"shine all over Equestria!"

151
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:10,650
Oh, Rarity, I was so worried
I'd ruined everything.

152
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:14,570
Oh, never.
I knew you'd be perfect.

153
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:17,030
[ Squealing and laughing ]

154
00:06:17,030 --> 00:06:19,030
[ Boing! Boing! Boing! Boing! ]

155
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:29,830
No. No. No.

156
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:30,960
Yes!

157
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,130
[ Tinkling ]

158
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:34,750
That is definitely
the one.

159
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,760
Photo Finish
is going to love it.

160
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:39,170
Everypony
is going to love it!

161
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:41,090
Oh, I am so excited
for you.

162
00:06:41,130 --> 00:06:43,510
Just don't forget
us little ponies

163
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:47,060
when you become the most famous
designer in all of Equestria.

164
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,060
Never.

165
00:06:48,060 --> 00:06:49,770
