Put me down here.

166
00:06:52,690 --> 00:06:54,730
[ Zip! ]

167
00:06:54,730 --> 00:06:57,070
Oh, no, no,
no, no, no, no. No.

168
00:06:57,110 --> 00:07:00,070
The model should be
in something simple!

169
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:02,700
Something inspired by...

170
00:07:02,740 --> 00:07:04,160
the nature.

171
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:08,040
That's just
what I was thinking.

172
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,580
Um, give me a moment
and I'll, uh,

173
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:13,040
put a little something
together.

174
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:15,460
Yes. That will not
be necessary.

175
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,550
But -- But --

176
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:19,880
How are you going to help me
"shine across Equestria"

177
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:23,010
If I don't design something new
for these pictures?

178
00:07:23,050 --> 00:07:25,890
I am not going to help you
shine across Equestria!

179
00:07:25,930 --> 00:07:28,890
I am going to help
her shine.

180
00:07:28,930 --> 00:07:31,140
She is my star!

181
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:32,770
You, go.

182
00:07:32,810 --> 00:07:34,810
[ Gasps ]

183
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,240
I can't, Rarity.

184
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,280
Oh, but you must,
Fluttershy.

185
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,830
Photo Finish
wants to make you a star.

186
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:50,250
This is the opportunity
of a lifetime.

187
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:53,250
I know we were both hoping
it would be my lifetime,

188
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:56,080
