194
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,640
[ Ting! ]

195
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:11,730
Oh, wunderbar!

196
00:08:11,770 --> 00:08:14,390
You are like
a delicate flower --

197
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:17,690
