with Fluttershy, not me.

203
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:34,040
Oh, Rarity.
I'm so sorry.

204
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,290
Is there anything
we can do?

205
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:40,170
I just...vant to be alone
right now.

206
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:46,010
