She "vants to be alone."

207
00:08:46,050 --> 00:08:48,010
[ Sproing! Sproing! ]

208
00:08:48,050 --> 00:08:49,180
[ Gasps ]

209
00:08:49,220 --> 00:08:52,680
What? I didn't think
she meant alone alone.

210
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,100
[ Sniffs ]

211
00:08:58,190 --> 00:08:59,650
[ Winces ]

212
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,990
Too much blush.

213
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:06,780
[ Rattle! ]

214
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:09,030
Not enough.

215
00:09:09,070 --> 00:09:10,160
Too much.

216
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,160
[ Winces ]

217
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,740
Not enough.

218
00:09:14,250 --> 00:09:16,210
Perfect.

219
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:19,920
Ah-ahhhhhh...

220
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:20,920
choo!

221
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,920
Oh, yes!

222
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,920
Even her schneezes
are graceful!

223
00:09:24,970 --> 00:09:26,050
Now go!

224
00:09:26,090 --> 00:09:27,340
[ Zip! ]

225
00:09:27,340 --> 00:09:29,930
