242
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,530
[ Crowd murmuring ]

243
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:40,870
[ Gasps ]

244
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,800
[ Growls ]

245
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:52,800
It's Fluttershy!

246
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,140
[ Ponies squealing ]

247
00:10:54,180 --> 00:10:56,010
Fluttershy!
Fluttershy!

248
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,350
Over here!

249
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,350
[ Camera shutters clicking ]

250
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,140
Fluttershy!
Over here!

251
00:11:00,190 --> 00:11:02,940
Beautiful, thank you.
Thank you.

252
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:03,940
Come here!

253
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:06,940
Right here, Fluttershy!
Over here!

254
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:08,940
