at the place!

267
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:40,310
I'll see you at the spa,
our usual time?

268
00:11:40,310 --> 00:11:41,140
Of course!

269
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:44,600
I can't wait to hear
all about the...

270
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,360
thing at the place.

271
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,280
[ Gasps ]

272
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,480
[ Grunts ]

273
00:11:49,530 --> 00:11:52,650
I'm the one who should be mobbed
by strangers wherever I go.

274
00:11:52,650 --> 00:11:54,030
[ Doorbell rings ]

275
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:57,330
Welcome
to carousel boutique!

276
00:11:57,370 --> 00:12:00,330
Is she still here?
We heard Fluttershy was here.

277
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:02,210
Sorry.
You just missed her.

278
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:04,080
But you're
still in luck.

279
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:07,170
I'm having a huge sale
on some of my best designs.

280
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:09,880
And you are?

281
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:11,470
Rarity, of course.

282
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:13,340
Never heard of you.

283
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,340
[ Growls ]

284
00:12:20,930 --> 00:12:24,640
Obviously, I, Photo Finish,
am thrilled to have found her.

285
00:12:24,690 --> 00:12:25,600
Photo Finish?

286
00:12:25,650 --> 00:12:28,270
She's a natural
in front of the camera.

287
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,070
Um, Photo Finish?

288
00:12:30,110 --> 00:12:31,990
I only need
to point and shoot,

289
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,030
and I capture...

290
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,030
the magics!

291
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:36,200
[ Indistinct shouting ]

292
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,370
Photo Finish,
I'm so sorry to interrupt.

293
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:40,330
It's just
that I'm running late.

294
00:12:40,370 --> 00:12:42,450
[ Gasps ]
How could I have forgotten?!

295
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:44,670
Your appearance
at the ballet opening --

296
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:47,960
Everypony who is anypony
will be there!

297
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:51,090
Oh, actually, I'm supposed to be
meeting my friend --

298
00:12:51,130 --> 00:12:52,130
We go!

299
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:56,050
[ Groans ]

300
00:12:56,090 --> 00:12:58,220
My hooves are getting
positively prune-y,

301
00:12:58,220 --> 00:13:00,180
I've been waiting here
so long.

302
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:04,690
Obviously, Fluttershy's just
too busy with her new career

303
00:13:04,730 --> 00:13:07,060
to spend time
with her best friend.

304
00:13:07,100 --> 00:13:09,270
I'm sure
she just got tied up.

305
00:13:09,310 --> 00:13:10,480
Of course she did.

306
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:12,690
She's a big, bright,
shining star.

307
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:15,490
I wish
that star would burn out!

308
00:13:15,530 --> 00:13:18,370
Rarity, Fluttershy
is your friend.

309
00:13:18,370 --> 00:13:19,410
I know! I know!

310
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:21,540
And I should be
happy for her,

311
00:13:21,580 --> 00:13:23,580
but instead,
I'm just...unh...jealous!

312
00:13:23,620 --> 00:13:26,420
Oh, please promise you won't
tell her I feel this way!

313
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:29,290
Please? Please?
Please, please, ple-e-ase?

314
00:13:29,330 --> 00:13:30,590
You have my word.

315
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:33,410
Losing a friend's trust is the
fastest way to lose a friend.

316
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:35,190
Forever!

317
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:43,350
Wow!
You look great!

318
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:45,600
Fluttershy may be
the one who's famous,

319
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:48,650
but that doesn't mean I have to
stop looking fabulous.

320
00:13:52,610 --> 00:13:56,070
Rarity,
I'm so sorry I'm --

321
00:13:56,110 --> 00:13:59,990
Oh, no.
She's already gone, isn't she?

322
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,330
Sorry.

323
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:03,330
Oh, I can't believe this.

324
00:14:03,370 --> 00:14:06,500
I am so frustrated,
I could just scream.

325
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:08,620
[ Inhales deeply ]

326
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:11,750
Aaaah...

327
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,750
Feel better?

328
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:16,050
[ Sighs ] No.

329
00:14:16,090 --> 00:14:18,090
Can I tell you
something?

330
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:18,880
Of course.

331
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:21,510
You promise
not to tell Rarity?

332
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:22,600
I swear.

333
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:24,140
Pinkie Pie swear?

334
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:25,770
Cross my heart
and hope to fly.

335
00:14:25,770 --> 00:14:27,640
Stick a cupcake
in my [screams]

336
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:32,310
I don't like
being a model.

337
00:14:32,310 --> 00:14:34,150
No, I hate
being a model.

338
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:36,320
All this attention is awful,
just awful!

339
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,280
And I'm only doing it

340
00:14:37,310 --> 00:14:41,180
because Rarity told me
I must, I must, I must.

341
00:14:41,490 --> 00:14:44,320
[ Sighs ] I must.

342
00:14:44,470 --> 00:14:46,140
Oh, really?

343
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:49,160
Well...

344
00:14:49,210 --> 00:14:51,580
if you want to know
the truth, Rarity --

345
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:52,630
[ Sproing! ]

346
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:56,090
[ Zip! ]

347
00:14:56,130 --> 00:14:57,800
W-what were you
about to say?

348
00:14:57,840 --> 00:15:00,380
Forever!

349
00:15:00,430 --> 00:15:01,760
Nothing.

350
00:15:05,890 --> 00:15:07,060
I was just thinking --

351
00:15:07,100 --> 00:15:11,310
If you really don't like being
a model, you could always quit.

352
00:15:11,350 --> 00:15:13,730
Oh, no. I could never
do such a thing.

353
00:15:13,770 --> 00:15:15,610
Rarity
would be devastated.

354
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:17,150
But Rarity told me --

355
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:18,570
[ Pop! ]
[ Gasps ]

356
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:30,500
Mmm! Juicy!

357
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:31,830
[ Groans ]

358
00:15:31,830 --> 00:15:34,880
Oh, if only all these ponies
didn't like me so much,

359
00:15:34,920 --> 00:15:37,960
Photo Finish wouldn't
want me to model anymore.

360
00:15:38,010 --> 00:15:39,880
She'd find
somepony else with...

361
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:41,430
the magic.

362
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:42,760
I guess you're right.

363
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:43,760
[ Ding! ]

364
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:45,100
You're right.

365
00:15:45,140 --> 00:15:47,680
You're right! You're right!
You're right!

366
00:15:47,680 --> 00:15:48,680
[ Crowd gasps ]

367
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:49,680
It's Fluttershy!

368
00:15:49,680 --> 00:15:51,770
[ Indistinct shouting ]

369
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:55,190
Don't you see?

370
00:15:55,230 --> 00:15:58,650
On her own, Fluttershy could
never do something unattractive.

371
00:15:58,690 --> 00:16:00,400
But if I use my magic
to help her

372
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,780
do something unattractive
at her next fashion show,

373
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:04,820
no one will ever
want her to model again.

374
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:07,030
And if Fluttershy
no longer has to be a model,

375
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:09,580
Rarity will no longer
have to be jealous of her.

376
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:11,830
And I'll no longer
have to keep their secrets!

377
00:16:11,870 --> 00:16:14,540
It's the perfect plan!
You can't tell anyone about it.

378
00:16:14,540 --> 00:16:16,920
Promise me
you won't tell anyone?!

379
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,800
[ Zip! ]

380
00:16:25,890 --> 00:16:28,850
So, you do promise
or you don't?

381
00:16:28,890 --> 00:16:29,890
Uh, yes!

382
00:16:29,930 --> 00:16:32,480
Obviously, that's why
I zipped my mouth closed,

383
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:33,640
then locked it with a key,

384
00:16:33,690 --> 00:16:35,560
then dug a hole,
then buried the key,

385
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:38,230
then built a house on top of the
hole where I buried the key,

386
00:16:38,230 --> 00:16:40,530
then moved into the house
on top of the hole!

387
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:42,490
Obviously.

388
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:44,490
[ Crowd murmuring ]

389
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:46,700
[ Electronic music playing ]

390
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:52,500
You really think
it'll work?

391
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:54,120
They love you
for being you,

392
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:56,750
so all I have to do
is make you not be you.

393
00:16:56,790 --> 00:16:57,960
Just leave it to me.

394
00:17:06,800 --> 00:17:09,970
I guess it's time to see
what all the fuss is about.

395
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,730
[ Tinkling ]

396
00:17:18,730 --> 00:17:20,110
[ Record scratches ]

397
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:21,980
[ Crowd gasps ]

398
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:23,530
[ Gasps ]

399
00:17:23,570 --> 00:17:24,530
[ Boing! ]

400
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:25,530
Uhhh...

401
00:17:25,570 --> 00:17:26,740
[ Honk! ]

402
00:17:26,780 --> 00:17:28,280
Aah!

403
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,080
[ Crowd gasps ]

404
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:32,240
[ Crowd gasps ]

405
00:17:35,910 --> 00:17:37,540
Aah!

406
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:39,170
[ Squeak! Squeak! ]

407
00:17:39,210 --> 00:17:40,840
[ Crowd gasps ]

408
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:46,130
[ Bark! Bark! ]

409
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:49,090
[ Crowd gasps ]

410
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:50,180
Oh, no.

411
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:52,720
[ Hee-haw! ]

412
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:53,970
[ Crowd booing ]

413
00:17:53,970 --> 00:17:55,730
Get her off the stage!

414
00:17:55,770 --> 00:17:58,690
She's an embarrassment
to all things fashion!

415
00:17:58,730 --> 00:18:01,690
I, Photo Finish,
have made a terrible mistake!

416
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:07,820
Rarity:
Bravo! I say, bravo!

417
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,860
Bravo?!

418
00:18:08,910 --> 00:18:12,660
Who could possibly say bravo
to that horrid display?

419
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:15,250
[ Rarity stomping ]
Such attitude!
Such pizzazz!

420
00:18:15,290 --> 00:18:17,870
She's invented an entirely
new kind of modeling!

421
00:18:17,910 --> 00:18:20,170
Who is saying
these things?

422
00:18:20,210 --> 00:18:21,840
[ Gasps ] It's her!

423
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:24,840
The unicorn in the gorgeous cape
and headdress.

424
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:27,170
Now, that is a pony
who clearly knows

425
00:18:27,220 --> 00:18:29,220
a thing or two
about fashion.

426
00:18:29,260 --> 00:18:33,310
Well, if that fabulous pony
likes it, then I do, too!

427
00:18:33,350 --> 00:18:34,310
Bravo!

428
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:35,310
Yes!

429
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:37,270
[ Crowd cheers ]

430
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,320
[ Sighs ]

431
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:50,070
This is awful.
Just awful.

432
00:18:50,110 --> 00:18:52,740
Somehow I've become
more popular than ever.

433
00:18:52,780 --> 00:18:56,370
Oh, I'm just so frustrated,
I could just kick something!

434
00:18:56,370 --> 00:18:58,910
[ Grunts gently ]

435
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:02,710
If only Rarity didn't want me
to be a model so badly.

436
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:04,710
[ Groans ]
But Rarity --

437
00:19:04,710 --> 00:19:05,710
[ Pop! ]

438
00:19:05,710 --> 00:19:08,340
Fluttershy!
Are you all right?

439
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:10,130
I'm great.

440
00:19:10,180 --> 00:19:12,890
I'm a super-famous
fashion model.

441
00:19:12,890 --> 00:19:14,890
Why wouldn't I
be great?

442
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:16,180
Because you ha--

443
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:18,890
Out there
on the runway,

444
00:19:18,930 --> 00:19:21,190
everyone was
turning on you, and --

445
00:19:21,190 --> 00:19:24,270
Oh, Fluttershy,
it's so awful.

446
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:26,070
I wanted them to.

447
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,610
You did?!

448
00:19:27,650 --> 00:19:30,700
Of course she did!
Because --

449
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:32,190
I'm jealous!

450
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,950
I wanted
all the attention,

451
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,660
and instead,
it was going to you.

452
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:37,740
I even started hoping that
you would do something silly

453
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:39,660
so your modeling career
would be over.

454
00:19:40,010 --> 00:19:42,430
But then,
when it started happening,

455
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:43,840
all I could think was,

456
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,440
"how could I
want you to fail

457
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:47,410
at something
you love so much?"

458
00:19:47,470 --> 00:19:49,340
But Fluttershy
doesn't --

459
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,140
[ Grunts ]

460
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:53,140
Love?

461
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:55,970
Oh, Rarity,
I hate being a model.

462
00:19:56,010 --> 00:19:56,970
You do?

463
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:58,220
More than anything.

464
00:19:58,270 --> 00:20:00,350
Then why
did you keep doing it?

465
00:20:00,390 --> 00:20:02,980
I was afraid if I quit,
you'd be mad at me

466
00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:05,810
for not wanting to
"shine all over Equestria."

467
00:20:05,860 --> 00:20:07,110
And I thought
if I told you

468
00:20:07,150 --> 00:20:08,860
how jealous I was
of your success,

469
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:10,650
you'd think
I was a terrible friend.

470
00:20:10,690 --> 00:20:11,650
Never.

471
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:12,780
All this time.

472
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:15,410
If we just told each other
the truth.

473
00:20:15,450 --> 00:20:18,740
I promise never to keep
my feelings a secret again.

474
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:19,620
Me too.

475
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:21,480
Both:
Cross my heart and hope to fly.

476
00:20:21,560 --> 00:20:23,150
Stick a cupcake in my eye.

477
00:20:23,290 --> 00:20:25,000
[ Both laugh ]

478
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:26,960
You were bwilliant!
Bwilliant!

479
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:29,090
I've already got
six photo shoots

480
00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:30,960
lined up
for tomorrow alone.

481
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:32,380
I'm sorry, Photo Finish,

482
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:35,760
but I don't think I'll be able
to make any of them.

483
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:37,180
Wha-a-t?

484
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,430
We go!
We go!

485
00:20:38,470 --> 00:20:41,220
[ Both laugh ]

486
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:43,810
Vhat has just happened?

487
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:44,810
[ Pop! ]

488
00:20:44,810 --> 00:20:46,980
Spike has a crush
on Rarity!

489
00:20:47,020 --> 00:20:48,150
[ Zip! ]

490
00:20:48,190 --> 00:20:51,150
[ Sighs ]
And you were doing so well.

491
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:55,450
Now, this is a wonderful way
to spend an afternoon.

492
00:20:55,490 --> 00:20:57,120
Isn't it, though?

493
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,870
Dear Princess Celestia,

494
00:20:58,910 --> 00:21:01,870
Being a good friend means
being able to keep a secret,

495
00:21:01,910 --> 00:21:03,370
but you should never be afraid

496
00:21:03,410 --> 00:21:06,080
to share your true feelings
with a good friend.

497
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,880
Did you get all that,
Spike?

498
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:10,000
No, I did not.

499
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:11,500
I still can't believe
you told someone

500
00:21:11,530 --> 00:21:13,220
about my secret feelings
for Rarity!

501
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:14,510
You're right.

502
00:21:15,010 --> 00:21:18,220
That was wrong of me,
and I'm very sorry.

503
00:21:18,260 --> 00:21:20,010
Apology accepted.

504
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:23,020
Now will you take down
my letter to Princess Celestia?

505
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:23,890
I would love to,

506
00:21:23,930 --> 00:21:27,850
but I'm a little busy
at the moment.

507
00:21:27,900 --> 00:21:30,900
[ Sighs ]

508
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:33,820
* My Little Pony

509
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,950
* My Little Pony

510
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:50,040
* My Little Pony

511
00:21:50,040 --> 00:21:54,050
* Friends

